data.title: Oscars 2024: ‘Oppenheimer’ wins best picture, capping off a big night for the Christopher Nolan film
data.meta_description: Will “Oppenheimer” take down “The Zone of Interest” for Best Picture? Can Lily Gladstone stave off Emma Stone in the Best Actress category? Join us as we provide commentary, analysis and more from the 96th Academy Awards.
